nodes.text: Handa Nobreg was a female scientist who lived during the time of the Galactic Civil War.

Dialogue pertaining to Handa Nobreg appeared in the directory tree files for the 2003 massively multiplayer online role-playing game Star Wars Galaxies: An Empire Divided. However, she never actually appeared on the video game's live servers as a proper non-player character.
